  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-2）：DeepSeek-V3.2 开源，DSA 稀疏注意力加持，算力与推理性能双突破",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500684&idx=1&sn=4909b3b0e70375a81eeb7b05837a8aa6",
  "date": "2025-12-02 09:19:00",
