  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：DeepSeek-V3.2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"342\" data-imgfileid=\"100017018\" data-ratio=\"0.29444444444444445\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d79656cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVdbclAlaicR2tDw3fyLupJVOoibTxX5Nco6j5I0Yf5BKcmWUmVq20SstmxncXJhJ5goETIQSvvibyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DeepSeek-V3.2 是一个结合高计算效率与卓越推理和Agent性能的模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。其创新点包括&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">DeepSeek Sparse Attention（DSA）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，一种优化长上下文场景的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">高效注意力机制</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">；可扩展的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">强化学习框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，使其性能与 GPT-5 相当；以及</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">大规模Agent任务合成管道</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，提升复杂交互环境中的合规性和泛化能力。该模型在 2025 年国际数学奥林匹克竞赛和国际信息学奥林匹克竞赛中获得金牌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepseek-v3-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepseek-v3-2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：AIA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"614\" data-imgfileid=\"100017021\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1170\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b8a716b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVdbclAlaicR2tDw3fyLupJLxKibZ90p796bwD8OyupvQxicpBriaN3vN7saicaxTb2V9PjPKZsZUWlVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AIA项目旨在通过分析多模态模型的底层机制，提出一种新的方法——注意力交互对齐（AIA），以解决生成任务和理解任务之间的冲突。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该方法在不需要架构解耦的情况下，通过在训练过程中显式约束交互模式，实现了在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Emu3和Janus-Pro</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">上的性能提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/aia3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/aia3</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：transformers</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"398\" data-imgfileid=\"100017020\" data-ratio=\"0.3416666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d662bf19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVdbclAlaicR2tDw3fyLupJeA2v69aUzVVEMG1N6LXSro78nyaib4vNm2aEQUA5S9gbXL8UKjQ2Thw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Transformers是一个用于定义和使用最先进的机器学习模型的框架，支持文本、视觉、音频和多模态模型的推理和训练。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">集中化的模型定义</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，确保与大多数训练框架和推理引擎的兼容性。Transformers致力于支持新兴的最先进模型，并通过简单、可定制和高效的模型定义来推动其使用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/transformers3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/transformers3</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Context-Aware Kernel Evolution（CAKE）</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"692\" data-imgfileid=\"100017019\" data-ratio=\"0.5935185185185186\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c592e54&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVdbclAlaicR2tDw3fyLupJWID1RCZFnyPvsG4aic8fMxcChERDXyAIiclZtlQfQE8uaaicV1Gf5FmtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Context-Aware Kernel Evolution(CAKE)是一个创新框架，利用大语言模型（LLMs）自适应地演化高斯过程核函数以进行贝叶斯优化。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">CAKE结合了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">进化算法</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">LLM推理</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，自动发现能够捕捉优化景观模式的核结构，从而无需手动干预即可实现问题特定的核结构选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/cake-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/cake-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：midday</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"588\" data-imgfileid=\"100017022\" data-ratio=\"0.5055555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd3d63a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVdbclAlaicR2tDw3fyLupJiaQarHPZXxeBXXCW6G2JjEibypLbGOAAOGs8bS2YYxNesu9PXh2B0x5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Midday 是一个为自由职业者、承包商、顾问和个体企业家设计的全能工具，旨在帮助他们更高效地管理业务运营。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它将通常分散在多个平台上的各种功能集成到一个统一的系统中，包括时间跟踪、发票管理、文件对账、存储和财务概览等功能。此外，Midday 还提供一个个性化的助手，帮助用户了解财务状况、优化支出并查找文件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/midday\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/midday</a>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：gi</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ga-world-0</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"380\" data-imgfileid=\"100017023\" data-ratio=\"0.3277777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e987fcb7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVdbclAlaicR2tDw3fyLupJxXro1poJR8KFfxOgTrSyBXnBa75SdGvgOdNl5JiaZgAicZV8xC45CFaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★GigaWorld-0是一个统一的世界模型框架，专为视觉-语言-动作（VLA）学习设计，作为数据引擎使用。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目集成了两个协同组件：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">GigaWorld-0-Video</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">GigaWorld-0-3D</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。GigaWorld-0-Video利用大规模视频生成技术，在外观、相机视角和动作语义的细粒度控制下，生成多样、纹理丰富且时间一致的序列。GigaWorld-0-3D结合了3D生成建模、3D高斯点云重建、物理可微系统识别和可执行运动规划，确保几何一致性和物理真实性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/giga-world-0\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/giga-world-0</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总了包括 DeepSeek-V3.2 大模型、AIA 多模态机制在内的最新开源 AI 项目，重点介绍其创新技术和应用潜力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总了包括 DeepSeek-V3.2 大模型、AIA 多模态机制在内的最新开源 AI 项目，重点介绍其创新技术和应用潜力。",
  "summary": "本文以“今日开源”的形式，快速介绍了多个近期发布的 AI 相关开源项目。核心内容包括：DeepSeek-V3.2 大模型，其通过 DeepSeek Sparse Attention（DSA）实现了计算效率和推理性能的突破，并具备强大的 Agent 能力；AIA 项目，旨在通过注意力交互对齐（AIA）解决多模态模型中生成与理解任务的冲突；Hugging Face 的 Transformers 框架，作为定义和使用先进机器学习模型的通用工具；CAKE 框架，利用 LLM 演化高斯过程核函数进行贝叶斯优化；GigaWorld-0，一个用于视觉-语言-动作（VLA）学习的统一世界模型框架。此外，文章还提及了一个与 AI 无关的自由职业者管理工具 Midday。整体而言，文章旨在为技术从业者提供快速了解最新 AI 开源动态的窗口。",
  "mainPoints": [
